  "description": "<h1>Ciudad Juárez-El Paso</h1>\n<h3>CJS · 1.0.0</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Subway-Builder-Modded/registry/refs/heads/main/maps/ciudad-juarez-el-paso/gallery/screenshot1.webp\" alt=\"Map Preview\"></p>\n<h2>Coverage</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Bounding box</strong></td><td>-106.68857, 31.49120, -106.12584, 32.04316</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Playable Area</strong></td><td>~3281 km²</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Population Summary</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Total Modeled Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,364,798</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Normal Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">1,234,198</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Modeled Special Demand</strong></td><td align=\"right\">130,600</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Map Statistics</h2>\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><td><strong>Demand Points</strong></td><td align=\"right\">2833</td></tr>\n<tr><td><strong>Populations</strong></td><td align=\"right\">40,921</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Special Demand</h2>\n<details>\n<summary>Airports — 13,400</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;CJS&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;5800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;ELP&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;7600&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Borders — 38,800</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;El Paso&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;26,000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Ysleta&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;12,800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Universities — 39,000</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Autónoma de Ciudad Juárez Instituto de Ciencias Sociales y Administración&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;5200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Autónoma de Ciudad Juárez Instituto de Ingeniería y Tecnología + Instituto de Arquitectura, Diseño y Arte&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;5000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Autónoma de Ciudad Juárez Instituto de Ciencias Biomédicas&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2400&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Autónoma de Ciudad Juárez Campus Ciudad Universitaria&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;4800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Instituto Tecnológico de Ciudad Juárez Campus I&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;2600&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Instituto Tecnológico de Ciudad Juárez Campus II&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Universidad Tecnológica de Ciudad Juárez&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;3800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;University of Texas at El Paso&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;12,600&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Southwest University&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Howard Payne University&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;275&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Western Technical College Main Campus&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;225&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Western Technical College Branch Campus&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;100&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Entertainment — 39,400</summary>\n\n<table style=\"width: auto\">\n<tr><th align=\"left\">Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Catedral de Nuestra Señora de Guadalupe y Mission de Guadalupe&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1900&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Monumento A La Mexicanidad&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1200&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Parque Público Federal El Chamizal&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;6000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Parque Central&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;6000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;La Rodadora Interactive Space&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;550&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Plaza Las Misiones&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;20,000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Centro Cultural Paso del Norte&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;700&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Estadio Olímpico Benito Juárez&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;800&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;El Paso Zoo and Botanical Gardens&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;1000&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Franklin Mountains State Park&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;350&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;El Paso Museum of Art&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;300&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Plaza Theatre&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;300&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;El Paso Museum of History&nbsp;&nbsp;</td><td align=\"right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;300&nbsp;&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<br>\n\n<h2>Additional Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Building Collision</strong> — A buildings index is included, providing in-game collision geometry for all non-filtered buildings.</li>\n<li><strong>Neighborhood Labels</strong> — The map includes municipal and neighborhood labels derived from administrative boundary data.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Methodology</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>MX data:<ul>\n<li>Processed INEGI&#39;s DENUE, CE, and CPV data sets for the entire country.</li>\n<li>Estimated business job counts by taking the geometric means of strata.</li>\n<li>Aggregated businesses to the block level.</li>\n<li>Estimated uncounted/informal jobs via the ENOE data set.</li>\n<li>Extracted relevant points for the bounding box of this map, then applied a modified version of Colin&#39;s gravity model.</li>\n<li>Added special demand via the Demand Adder.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>US data:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rslurry/subwaybuilder-US-demand-data\">subwaybuilder-US-demand-generator</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Border data:<ul>\n<li>Assumes 50% of crossing happen from US side, and 50% happen from MX side. Values rounded down to ensure an equal number of pops for both.  Commutes to/from the border point are separately done for MX and US sub-maps (where pops live/work at the border crossing and work/live somewhere in the city), then pops are paired up to form commutes from MX to US and vice versa.  A 30 minute border crossing time penalty is applied to the commute.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Data Sources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/programas/ce/2024/\">INEGI Censos Económicos (CE) 2024</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/app/mapa/denue/default.aspx\">INEGI Directorio Estadístico Nacional de Unidades Económicas (DENUE)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/programas/ccpv/2020/\">INEGI Censo de Población y Vivienda (CPV) 2020</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.inegi.org.mx/programas/enoe/15ymas/\">INEGI Encuesta Nacional de Ocupación y Empleo (ENOE)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://lehd.ces.census.gov/data/\">US Census Bureau LEHD Origin-Destination Employment Statistics (LODES)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://data.bts.gov/stories/s/jswi-2e7b\">US Bureau of Transportation Statistics Border Crossing/Entry Data</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>License</h2>\n<p>This map data is released under the <a href=\"https://github.com/ahkimn/subwaybuilder-jp-maps/blob/main/LICENSE\">GNU General Public License v3.0</a>.</p>\n<h2>Credits</h2>\n<p>Map authored by slurry</p>",
